		 	  DVK500				 STK16+
				CS		---------	  VCC
				PSB	    ---------	  GND
				SID		---------	  PB2
				CLK		---------	  PB1				
				
		 	  DVK500				 STK16+
				VCC		---------	  VCC
				GND		---------	  GND
				/MR	    ---------	  VCC
				A/B		---------	  PB1
				CLK		---------	  PB0
